  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/768feeb999b55ab09f13efa0f018d9d1.poster.avif?t=1765353239\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/768feeb999b55ab09f13efa0f018d9d1.webm?t=1765353239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/768feeb999b55ab09f13efa0f018d9d1.mp4?t=1765353239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to the South Pole, where you will have to lift penguins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Penguin Helper </strong>is a fun 3D first-person game in which you become a real hero to these funny creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/e692fc9cafdc880191bfd806f8c1ee64.poster.avif?t=1765353239\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/e692fc9cafdc880191bfd806f8c1ee64.webm?t=1765353239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/e692fc9cafdc880191bfd806f8c1ee64.mp4?t=1765353239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a walk among the snowy open spaces and watch the southern lights. But be careful! Penguins lose coordination as soon as a plane flies over them. Your task is to put them on their feet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/a24d4e7c4b54e9228ea5f4e03e2b1c47.poster.avif?t=1765353239\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/a24d4e7c4b54e9228ea5f4e03e2b1c47.webm?t=1765353239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/a24d4e7c4b54e9228ea5f4e03e2b1c47.mp4?t=1765353239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore frosty landscapes, enjoy the beauty of vast expanses and skies, and enjoy the calm and tranquility of the South Pole.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/46c299aea8439db1da6b2dca4960fff1.poster.avif?t=1765353239\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/46c299aea8439db1da6b2dca4960fff1.webm?t=1765353239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/46c299aea8439db1da6b2dca4960fff1.mp4?t=1765353239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The breathtaking expanses of the South Pole</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Interaction with penguins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Raising penguins as the main mechanic of the game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Meditative atmosphere with pleasant sound</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Counter of raised penguins</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/76e7e6994be568213d847be96308ac19.avif?t=1765353239\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to become a real hero of the South Pole? Put on warm clothes, stock up on tea and start your Penguin Helper adventure![/IMG][]</p>",
